magik is a highly customizable tool to create password-less login experiences.
The authentication parts can be swapped out for a different approach or even multiple where possible.

Ideas:
  - interchangeable token generation algorithm
  - interchangealbe token storage (memory, local, redis)
  - interchangeable array of sending techniques (email (stmp, mail services), sms etc)
  - various providers for different routing libraries in go (net/http, gin, muxie)
